Encryption: Testing Plan

List your test cases below. 

Tests:
Encryption tests:

1. Short lowercase input 
    
This test checks to make sure the program handles a short input containing only lowercase letters.
Input: "helloworld"
Expected Output:
n = 0: helloworld
n = 1: ifmmpxpsme
n = 2: jgnnqyqtnf
n = 3: khoorzruog
n = 4: lippsasvph
n = 5: mjqqtbtwqi
n = 6: nkrrucuxrj
n = 7: olssvdvysk
n = 8: pmttwewztl
n = 9: qnuuxfxaum
n = 10: rovvygybvn
n = 11: spwwzhzcwo
n = 12: tqxxaiadxp
n = 13: uryybjbeyq
n = 14: vszzckcfzr
n = 15: wtaadldgas
n = 16: xubbemehbt
n = 17: yvccfnficu
n = 18: zwddgogjdv
n = 19: axeehphkew
n = 20: byffiqilfx
n = 21: czggjrjmgy
n = 22: dahhksknhz
n = 23: ebiiltloia
n = 24: fcjjmumpjb
n = 25: gdkknvnqkc

2. Input with spaces and capital letters
This test checks to make sure the program handles a input containing spaces and uppercase letters.
Input: "Hello World"
Expected Output:
n = 0: Hello
n = 1: Hfmmp
n = 2: Hgnnq
n = 3: Hhoor
n = 4: Hipps
n = 5: Hjqqt
n = 6: Hkrru
n = 7: Hlssv
n = 8: Hmttw
n = 9: Hnuux
n = 10: Hovvy
n = 11: Hpwwz
n = 12: Hqxxa
n = 13: Hryyb
n = 14: Hszzc
n = 15: Htaad
n = 16: Hubbe
n = 17: Hvccf
n = 18: Hwddg
n = 19: Hxeeh
n = 20: Hyffi
n = 21: Hzggj
n = 22: Hahhk
n = 23: Hbiil
n = 24: Hcjjm
n = 25: Hdkkn

Explaination:
The program should truncate the space and not change any character that is not lowercase.

